<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>	<item><status>past</status><description>On Tuesday, Ray and I took a glorious ride up to VT heading up Rt 119 to Rt 9 in Vermont and back via Rt 91 to Rt 2. It was an amazing ride.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;I want to do it again, but this time in somewhat in reverse , and starting earlier.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Next Wednesday is expected to be in the 60's both here and up there.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Plan is to leave at 8AM sharp from the rotary in Concord and get up to Wilmington for lunch at noon, scoot west and then south to Williamstown, then back on Rt 2 to Boston. Total road time, about 7 hours (280 Miles) with lunch and stops along the way we should be back by sunset.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;I will firm up plans on Monday weather wise and if it gets canceled for any reason, we will be sure to do it the following week or the week after.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Here's the proposed route: &lt;a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=d&amp;amp;hl=en&amp;amp;geocode=5092032762308928941,42.598990,-72.382100%3B6674821778167919761,43.057630,-72.944670%3B10137904961984459757,43.194020,-72.954010%3B13899094752082422494,42.628110,-72.886840%3B15027786783264712260,42.591860,-72.445380&amp;amp;saddr=2345+Commonwealth+Ave,+Auburndale,+MA+02466&amp;amp;daddr=E+Main+St%2FMohawk+Trail%2FRT-2+%4042.598990,+-72.382100+to:Wilmington,+VT,+USA+to:Stratton-Arlington+Rd+%4043.057630,+-72.944670+to:43.074907,-73.02063+to:Bennington,+Vt+to:Williamstown,+MA+to:Mohawk+Trail%2FRT-2+%4042.628110,+-72.886840+to:Mohawk+Trail%2FRT-2+%4042.591860,+-72.445380+to:2345+Commonwealth+Ave,+Auburndale,+MA+02466&amp;amp;mra=dme&amp;amp;mrcr=1&amp;amp;mrsp=4&amp;amp;sz=9&amp;amp;via=1,3,4,7,8&amp;amp;jsv=107&amp;amp;sll=42.761129,-72.204895&amp;amp;sspn=1.502273,2.886658&amp;amp;ie=UTF8&amp;amp;t=p&amp;amp;z=9" target="_blank"&gt;MAP&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;</description><event_hosts><event_hosts_item><member_name>Paul Shoemaker</member_name><member_id>3108784</member_id>